From 4ce79fa97e6a54ee028063381346dc2fea91a76b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dan Williams <dan.j.williams@intel.com>
Date: Tue, 12 Nov 2019 17:07:39 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] libnvdimm: Move nd_mapping_attribute_group to device_type
Git-commit: 4ce79fa97e6a54ee028063381346dc2fea91a76b
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-13338

A 'struct device_type' instance can carry default attributes for the
device. Use this facility to remove the export of
nd_mapping_attribute_group and put the responsibility on the core rather
than leaf implementations to define this attribute.

